                options: ["192", "71", "96", "142"],
                correct: "C",
            },
            {
                id: 4,
                type: "mcq",
                text: `If the sum of the first 10 terms of the series 1¬≤ + 2 + 3¬≤ + 4 + ... is 135, then m is equal to`,
