                correct: "B",
            },
            {
                id: 5,
                type: "mcq",
                text: `Let A be sum of first 20 and B be sum of first 40 terms of series 1¬≤/2¬≤ + 3¬≤/4¬≤ + ... If B - 2A = 1000, then a is`,
                options: ["496", "232", "248", "464"],
                correct: "C",
            },
            {
                id: 6,
                type: "mcq",
                text: `Let S = 1 + q + q¬≤ + ... + q^n and Tn = 1 + q + 1/2 + ... where q is real number ‚â† 1. If T100 = sum involving binomial coefficients, then a is equal to`,
                options: ["200"],
                correct: "A",
            },
            {
                id: 7,
                type: "mcq",
                text: `The sum of all natural numbers n such that 100 < n < 200 and H.C.F. (91, n) > 1 is`,
                options: ["3203", "3221", "3121", "3303"],
                correct: "C",
            },
            {
                id: 8,
                type: "mcq",
                text: `Let a‚ÇÅ, a‚ÇÇ, ... be an A.P. with a‚ÇÅ=2. The common difference maximizing a‚ÇÅ‚ÇÇ √ó a‚ÇÑ‚ÇÇ √ó a‚ÇÖ‚ÇÇ is`,
                options: ["3/8", "5", "2/3", "6/5"],
                correct: "B",
            },
            {
                id: 9,
                type: "mcq",
                text: `Let f:R‚ÜíR such that for all x ‚àà R, f(x), 2|x|+1, 3x+3 are in A.P. Minimum value of f(x) is`,
                options: ["2", "4", "0", "3"],
                correct: "D",
            },
            {
                id: 10,
                type: "mcq",
                text: `Let S be sum of first 9 terms of series {x + k*a} + {x¬≤ + (k+2)*a} + ... If S = x - 1, then k is equal to`,
